            "id": "https://starofeden.github.io/2023/11/10/mysql%E5%A4%8D%E4%B9%A0/",
            "url": "https://starofeden.github.io/2023/11/10/mysql%E5%A4%8D%E4%B9%A0/",
            "title": "mysql语句总结",
            "date_published": "2023-11-09T16:00:00.000Z",
            "content_html": "<h1 id=\"课堂复习题\"><a href=\"#课堂复习题\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"课堂复习题\"></a>课堂复习题</h1><blockquote>\n<p>已知三张表如下:<br>学生(学号、姓名、班级、年龄)<br>课程(课号、课名、学分)<br>选课(学号、课号、成绩)<br>请完成以下练习题:<br>1、把数据库原理及应用课程成绩增加10分。<br>2、删除李四同学的选课记录。<br>3、 显示数据库原理及应用的学生成绩<br>4、查询每个学生选修课程的学号、课程名称和成绩。<br>5、查询每个同学的学号，姓名，总学分。(成绩及格的才能拿到学分)<br>6、找出每个学生超过他所有的选修课程的平均成绩的课程号。<br>7、查询每个班、每门课程的平均分</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>1.把数据库原理及应用课程成绩增加10分。<br><figure class=\"highlight sql\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">UPDATE</span> 选课  </span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">SET</span> 成绩 <span class=\"operator\">=</span> 成绩 <span class=\"operator\">+</span> <span class=\"number\">10</span>  </span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">WHERE</span> 课号 <span class=\"operator\">=</span> (<span class=\"keyword\">SELECT</span> 课号 <span class=\"keyword\">FROM</span> 课程 <span class=\"keyword\">WHERE</span> 课名 <span class=\"operator\">=</span> <span class=\"string\">&#x27;数据库原理及应用&#x27;</span>);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>\n<p>2.删除李四同学的选课记录<br><figure class=\"highlight sql\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">DELETE</span> <span class=\"keyword\">FROM</span> 选课  </span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">WHERE</span> 学号 <span class=\"operator\">=</span> (<span class=\"keyword\">SELECT</span> 学号 <span class=\"keyword\">FROM</span> 学生 <span class=\"keyword\">WHERE</span> 姓名 <span class=\"operator\">=</span> <span class=\"string\">&#x27;李四&#x27;</span>);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><br>3.显示数据库原理及应用的学生成绩<br><figure class=\"highlight sql\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">SELECT</span> 学生.学号, 学生.姓名, 选课.成绩   </span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">FROM</span> 学生   </span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">JOIN</span> 选课 <span class=\"keyword\">ON</span> 学生.学号 <span class=\"operator\">=</span> 选课.学号   </span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">JOIN</span> 课程 <span class=\"keyword\">ON</span> 选课.课号 <span class=\"operator\">=</span> 课程.课号   </span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">WHERE</span> 课程.课名 <span class=\"operator\">=</span> <span class=\"string\">&#x27;数据库原理及应用&#x27;</span>;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><br>4.查询每个学生选修课程的学号、课程名称和成绩。<br><figure class=\"highlight sql\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">select</span> 学生.学号, 课程.课名, 选课.成绩</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">FROM</span> 学生   </span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">JOIN</span> 选课 <span class=\"keyword\">ON</span> 学生.学号 <span class=\"operator\">=</span> 选课.学号   </span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">JOIN</span> 课程 <span class=\"keyword\">ON</span> 选课.课号 <span class=\"operator\">=</span> 课程.课号</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>\n<h1 id=\"多表查询\"><a href=\"#多表查询\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"多表查询\"></a>多表查询</h1><p>1.查询每个同学的总学分，成绩大于等于60才能拿到学分，以中文显示学号、姓名、总学分，以学号升序排列。<br><figure class=\"highlight sql\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">select</span> s.sno <span class=\"keyword\">as</span> 学号, s.sn <span class=\"keyword\">as</span> 姓名, coalesec(<span class=\"built_in\">sum</span>(credit)) <span class=\"keyword\">as</span> 总学分</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">from</span> s</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">left</span> <span class=\"keyword\">join</span> sc <span class=\"keyword\">on</span> s.sno <span class=\"operator\">=</span> sc.sno</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">left</span> <span class=\"keyword\">join</span> c <span class=\"keyword\">on</span> sc.cno <span class=\"operator\">=</span> c.cno <span class=\"keyword\">and</span> sc.score<span class=\"operator\">&gt;=</span><span class=\"number\">60</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">group</span> <span class=\"keyword\">by</span> 学号,姓名</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">order</span> <span class=\"keyword\">by</span> 总学分;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>\n<h1 id=\"group-by与order-by\"><a href=\"#group-by与order-by\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"group by与order by\"></a>group by与order by</h1><figure class=\"highlight sql\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">select</span> c.cno, c.cn, <span class=\"built_in\">count</span>(s.sno)</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">from</span> c</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">left</span> <span class=\"keyword\">join</span> sc <span class=\"keyword\">on</span> c.cno <span class=\"operator\">=</span> sc.cno</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">left</span> <span class=\"keyword\">join</span> s <span class=\"keyword\">on</span> sc.cno <span class=\"operator\">=</span> s.sno</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">group</span> <span class=\"keyword\">by</span> c.cno, c.cn</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">order</span> <span class=\"keyword\">by</span> c.cno</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h1 id=\"having\"><a href=\"#having\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"having\"></a>having</h1><span class='p red'>group by 要写在having前面</span>\n<figure class=\"highlight sql\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">select</span> s.sno, s.sn, <span class=\"built_in\">avg</span>(score)</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">from</span> s</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">join</span> sc <span class=\"keyword\">on</span> s.sno <span class=\"operator\">=</span> sc.sno</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">GROUP</span> <span class=\"keyword\">BY</span> s.sno, s.sn  </span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">HAVING</span> <span class=\"built_in\">AVG</span>(sc.score) <span class=\"operator\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"number\">80</span>  </span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">order</span> <span class=\"keyword\">by</span> s,sno</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h1 id=\"左连接中显示出null值\"><a href=\"#左连接中显示出null值\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"左连接中显示出null值\"></a>左连接中显示出null值</h1><ul>\n<li><span class='p red'>加一个coalesce()</span>\n<figure class=\"highlight sql\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">SELECT</span> s.sno <span class=\"keyword\">as</span> 学号, s.sn <span class=\"keyword\">as</span> 姓名, <span class=\"built_in\">COALESCE</span>(<span class=\"built_in\">SUM</span>(c.credit)) <span class=\"keyword\">AS</span> 总学分 </span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">FROM</span> s </span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">LEFT</span> <span class=\"keyword\">JOIN</span> sc <span class=\"keyword\">ON</span> s.sno <span class=\"operator\">=</span> sc.sno </span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">LEFT</span> <span class=\"keyword\">JOIN</span> c <span class=\"keyword\">ON</span> sc.cno <span class=\"operator\">=</span> c.cno <span class=\"keyword\">AND</span> sc.score <span class=\"operator\">&gt;=</span> <span class=\"number\">60</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">GROUP</span> <span class=\"keyword\">BY</span> s.sno, s.sn</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">ORDER</span> <span class=\"keyword\">BY</span> s.sno <span class=\"keyword\">ASC</span>;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h1 id=\"基本操作\"><a href=\"#基本操作\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"基本操作\"></a>基本操作</h1><h2 id=\"update\"><a href=\"#update\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"update\"></a>update</h2></li>\n<li><span class='p red'>这里字段内容加单引号，id的值都是int不加单引号</span>\n<figure class=\"highlight sql\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">update</span> <span class=\"keyword\">from</span> tb_emp</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">set</span> Name <span class=\"operator\">=</span> <span class=\"string\">&#x27;Tracy&#x27;</span>, DeptId <span class=\"operator\">=</span> <span class=\"string\">&#x27;302&#x27;</span>, <span class=\"string\">&#x27;Salary&#x27;</span> <span class=\"operator\">=</span> <span class=\"string\">&#x27;4300&#x27;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">where</span> id <span class=\"operator\">=</span> <span class=\"number\">3</span>;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h2 id=\"delete\"><a href=\"#delete\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"delete\"></a>delete</h2><figure class=\"highlight sql\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">delete</span> <span class=\"keyword\">from</span> tb_emp <span class=\"keyword\">where</span> Salary<span class=\"operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"number\">3000</span>;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h2 id=\"alter\"><a href=\"#alter\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"alter\"></a>alter</h2><span class='p red'>alter用来修改表名或者字段名</span>\n<figure class=\"highlight sql\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">ALTER</span> <span class=\"keyword\">TABLE</span> testalter_tbl <span class=\"keyword\">ADD</span> i <span class=\"type\">INT</span>;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>\n</ul>\n",
            "tags": [
                "mysql"
            ]
        }
    ]
}